:R-HSA-8849468  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0008150 ;
        rdfs:comment        "PTK6 binds and phosphorylates several nuclear RNA-binding proteins, including SAM68 family members (KHDRSB1, KHDRSB2 and KHDRSB3) (Derry et al. 2000, Haegebarth et al. 2004, Lukong et al. 2005) and SFPQ (PSF) (Lukong et al. 2009). The biological role of PTK6 in RNA processing is not known." ;
        rdfs:label          "PTK6 Regulates Proteins Involved in RNA Processing" ;
        dc:contributor      "Reviewed: Pires, Isabel M, 2016-02-07" , "Authored: Orlic-Milacic, Marija, 2016-01-04" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Edited: Orlic-Milacic, Marija, 2016-01-04" ;
